snippet.title: Boonieverse Official Trailer - from the creators of MovieStarPlanet
snippet.description:
Download it here: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id669020618

Explore a fantastic new world where you battle and collect adorable monsters called Boonies! Feed them, wash them, and play with them to keep them happy! 

Create your own legendary family of Boonies that will be known and admired throughout the Boonieverse!

From the creators of MovieStarPlanet. 

http://apps.moviestarplanet.com/boonieverse/

Download it here: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id669020618
